{"tid":1329252,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣可以冇咁怕醜","createTime":"2019-07-18T07:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T16:16:38.000Z","uid":144559,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7af898bca7e8e2289eab342ba9127f78ebcd8c","tid":1329252,"uid":144559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:02:21.000Z","msg":"講下背景<br />\n細個性格好孤僻 小學冇朋友<br />\n唔會同人講野<br />\n試過中一因爲好靜俾人恰<br />\n<br />\n後尾有個人主動同我做朋友<br />\n慢慢都開始有正常社交<br />\n到依家都有幾個社交圈子<br />\n<br />\n但當我以爲自己比較social嗰陣<br />\n對住陌生人都係好怕醜<br />\n搵咩工都好都好怕醜好易緊張<br />\n對住唔熟既人又好靜<br />\n<br />\n發現咁落去<br />\n明明覺得自己有能力有實力<br />\n啲人都會當左我廢<br />\n因為我唔識向住佢地有自信咁表達 好易緊張<br />\n<br />\n點算啊<br />\n已經失業咗兩個月 <br />\n就算有啲料到 都唔夠班outgoing既人嚟"},{"pid":"d5b2edc86001e07ddc9fe045b0f9f8e4f97cc891","tid":1329252,"uid":144559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc87ed1ff08a0520a6eb779e2d7c8e4076c779bb","tid":1329252,"uid":201212,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:08:21.000Z","msg":"打破零的回覆"},{"pid":"03fb59f0ac5b6da9085941c1dc58fa7dd95befec","tid":1329252,"uid":144559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm